<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>TSI 92-12-11 - Release of Segmented Oil Pan Gaskets for DT/DTA-360 and DT/DTA-466 Diesel Engines.</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi921211" tsitype="truck">
        <tsinumber>92-12-11</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>June, 1992</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>ENGINE</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Release of Segmented Oil Pan Gaskets for DT/DTA-360 and DT/DTA-466 Diesel Engines.</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <apply>
            <configure>
                <engfamgroup/>

                <engfam>DT 360</engfam>
                <engfam>DTA 360</engfam>
                <engfam>DT 466</engfam>
                <engfam>DTA 466</engfam>
            </configure>
        </apply>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>One piece oil pan gaskets used on DT/DTA-360 and DT/DTA-466 diesel engines are replaced with a new
                    four piece segmented oil pan gasket for service. Refer to
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9212111">Figure 1</hotlnk>.
                </para>
                <figure id="f9212111" figsize="pg-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/G9212111.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 1. Oil Pan Gasket Comparison</caption>
                </figure>
                <para>Gasket part numbers are advanced to "C3" to identify change. Refer to
                    <hotlnk xrefid="t9212111">Table 1</hotlnk>
                    below.
                </para>
                <table id="t9212111" frame="all">
                    <title>Gasket Part Numbers</title>
                    <tgroup cols="3" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <colspec colwidth="1.83in"/>
                        <colspec colwidth="1.83in"/>
                        <colspec colwidth="1.83in"/>
                        <thead>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Engine Model</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Displaced One Piece Gasket P/N</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Advanced Four Piece Segmented Gasket P/N</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>DT/DTA-360</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>671 825 C2</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>671 825 C3</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>DT/DTA-466</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>671 827 C2</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>671 827 C3</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                    </tgroup>
                </table>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>Four piece segmented oil pan gasket is serviced individually and in various packages.
                            Package part numbers also are advanced to identify gasket change. Refer to Parts Affected (
                            <hotlnk xrefid="t9212112">Table 2</hotlnk>) for service part numbers of packages.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
                <para>When new four piece segmented oil pan gasket, P/N 671 825 C3 or 671 827 C3 is ordered for service,
                    it is to be noted that gasket will be shipped, disassembled and packaged as shown in
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9212112">Figure 2.</hotlnk>
                </para>
                <figure id="f9212112" figsize="pg-wide">
                    <graphic filename="../tsifigures/G9212112.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 2. Packaging Detail For Segmented Oil Pan Gasket, P/N 671 825 C3 Or 671 827 C3
                    </caption>
                </figure>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
