        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="1">
            <title>ASSEMBLY INSTRUCTIONS</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Separate segments at the serrations (represented by dotted lines in Packing Detail
                    illustration,
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9212112">Figure 2</hotlnk>).
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Place a small amount of an automotive type RTV, aviation permatex or equivalent sealant
                    on tabs and anchors of each gasket segment.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Matching alpha letter (A to B; C to D: etc.); install tab ends into anchor ends of
                    gasket segments. Refer to
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f9212113">Figure 3</hotlnk>.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f9212113" figsize="pg-wide">
